   [[!cve CVE-2020-15852]], [[!cve CVE-2020-10781]],
   [[!cve CVE-2020-10781]], [[!cve CVE-2020-15780]]
 - Evolution Data Server: [[!debsa2020 4725]]
 - FFmpeg: [[!debsa2020 4722]]
 - ImageMagick: [[!debsa2020 4712]]
 - NSS: [[!debsa2020 4726]]
 - OpenMPT: [[!debsa2020 4729]]
 - WebKitGTK: [[!debsa2020 4724]]
